Whether working to secure a large event or responsible for the ongoing safety of visitors at a transport hub, the frontlines of ground level threat detection face an ever-evolving environment.

WWT's Mobile Field Kit (MFK) allows public safety personnel to access threat information, situational awareness and update alerts by a central command center as well as via mobile devices or tablets on the ground.
Mobile Field Kit is our operations control + threat monitoring system that can assist those responsible for public safety at events, places of interest, entertainment venues to secure the perimeter.
